1. Pitao *sam* da li si se dobro proveo. (I *asked* if you had a good time.)
2. *Pitaš* li da li treba da ponesem nešto? (Are you *asking* if I should bring something?)
3. On me *pitaju* da li mogu da dođu. (They are *asking* me if they can come.)
4. Ona *pita* da li će se moći osloniti na mene. (She is *asking* if she can rely on me.)
5. Mi smo se *pitali* da li će biti vremena za odmor. (We were *wondering* if there would be time for a break.)